📖 Clinic Management System for Biruk Clinic <a name="about-the-project"></a>
The Clinic Management System for Biruk Clinic is designed to streamline clinic operations through a user-friendly interface. It provides secure authentication and a comprehensive management system where the admin can manage doctors and patients, and patients can book appointments and view prescriptions.

🛠 Built With <a name="built-with"></a>
Tech Stack <a name="tech-stack"></a>
Front-end: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Back-end: PHP
Key Features <a name="key-features"></a>
User Authentication: Secure login and registration functionality.
Admin Dashboard: Admins can add doctors, manage patients, and accept bookings.
Patient Portal: Patients can register, book appointments, and view prescriptions.
Doctor Interface: Doctors can accept bookings and add reports.
